Text.val: parameter is used for changed temporary records
which were saved in TEMP, left to other online program
and came back without any action
1 small table
2 large table
3 switch small / large table
don't locate by refreshing window
init program
set what to do to go out if nothing of the below statements fit
if called from RP call online and end
if called from main
no records exists go create
number of existing lines smaller then maximal lines
goto small table
number of existing lines bigger then maximal lines
goto big table
small Table
close previous screen
large Table
close previous screen
create New
Edit Current
Delete Current
-- Check for existing COUT rows where COUT202_REPORTTYPE =OPL
... at least one COUT row for OPL reports needs to remain
delete Yes
exit program - close large table and open small one
